{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idee9cc1dc-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1429"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1429"},"text":"§ 1429.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Determinations of Secretary as final and conclusive","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Determinations made by the Secretary under this Act shall be final and conclusive: ","children":[{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"Provided","children":[],"tail":", That the scope and nature of such determinations shall not be inconsistent with the provisions of the Commodity Credit Corporation Charter Act ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s714"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 714","children":[],"tail":" et seq.]."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idee9cc1dd-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1949-10-31/ch792"},"text":"Oct. 31, 1949, ch. 792","children":[],"tail":", title IV, § 412, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/63/1057"},"text":"63 Stat. 1057","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idee9cc1de-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idee9cc1df-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idee9cc1e0-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This Act, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1949-10-31/ch792"},"text":"act Oct. 31, 1949, ch. 792","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/63/1051"},"text":"63 Stat. 1051","children":[],"tail":", known as the Agricultural Act of 1949, which is classified principally to this chapter (§ 1421 et seq.). For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1421"},"text":"section 1421 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Commodity Credit Corporation Charter Act, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1948-06-29/ch704"},"text":"act June 29, 1948, ch. 704","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/62/1070"},"text":"62 Stat. 1070","children":[],"tail":", as amended, which is classified generally to subchapter II (§ 714 et seq.) of chapter 15 of Title 15, Commerce and Trade. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s714"},"text":"section 714 of Title 15","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
